'title':
 """
    Verify block crypto algorithms that are implemented in ENCRYPT/DECRYPT built-in functions.
    See doc\sql.extensions\README.builtin_functions.txt for details.

    Checked on 4.0.0.1691: OK, 1.561s.
 """,
